    Rayleigh wave, Love wave, group wave, phase wave, earthquake focus, hypocenter, 
    earthquake epicentra, earthquake magnitude, seismic moment, moment magnitude, 
    EQ Intensity, aftershocks, foreshocks, swarms, Young's modulus, Poisson's 
    ration, free oscillation, torsional, toroidal oscillation, spheroidal oscillation, 
    travel-time curve, shadow zone, seismic phase,


















地球物理學概論








