週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Course overview2Elastic-Brittle-Viscous material3Gravity (I)4Gravity (II)5Geodesy (I)6Geodesy (II)7Seismic (I)8Seismic (II)9midterm exam10Earthquake (I)11Earthquake (II)12Seismic Reflection13Seismic Refraction14Electric15Magnetic16Heat Flow17Geophysics in Taiwan18Final exam 

